  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">SkyGrid — Skyscrapers Puzzle &middot; Last updated: March 22, 2026</p>

  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>
    SkyGrid ("we", "our", "the app") is a mobile logic puzzle game developed as a personal project.
    We are committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what data the app collects (or doesn't collect)
    and how it operates.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Data Collection</h2>
  <p><strong>SkyGrid does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data.</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>No account or registration is required.</li>
    <li>No email addresses, names, or identifiers are collected.</li>
    <li>No analytics or tracking tools are used.</li>
    <li>No cookies are used.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Local Storage</h2>
  <p>
    The app stores your game progress (puzzle state, settings, daily history) locally on your device
    using the browser's <code>localStorage</code> API. This data:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Never leaves your device.</li>
    <li>Is not accessible to us or any third party.</li>
    <li>Can be cleared at any time by clearing the app's data in your device settings.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>
    SkyGrid does not currently integrate any third-party services such as advertising networks,
    analytics platforms, or social media SDKs. If this changes in the future, this policy will be updated accordingly.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    SkyGrid does not knowingly collect any information from children under 13.
    The app does not require any personal information to function.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Permissions</h2>
  <p>SkyGrid requires the following device permissions:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Internet Access:</strong> Required only for loading the initial web assets. No data is sent to external servers.</li>
    <li><strong>Vibration:</strong> Used for optional haptic feedback during gameplay. Can be disabled in app settings.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page
    with an updated "Last updated" date. Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance
    of the revised policy.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Contact</h2>
  <p>
    If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at:
    <br />
    <a href="mailto:skygrid.app@gmail.com">skygrid.app@gmail.com</a>
  </p>

